              "  'content': '<Card title=\"Evidently Cloud - Migration guide\" href=\"/faq/cloud_v2\">\\n  What\\'s new in Evidently Cloud v2.\\n</Card>\\n\\n<Card title=\"Evidently library - Migration guide\" href=\"/faq/migration\">\\n  How to migrate to a new Evidently 0.6 version and above.\\n</Card>\\n\\n<Card title=\"OSS vs Cloud\" href=\"/faq/oss_vs_cloud\">\\n  Understand feature availability.\\n</Card>\\n\\nUse the menu on the left to explore other questions.',\n",
